Name: Fresh and Icy Special Commemorative Can
Desc: Fresh and Icy Energy Drink Special's limited-edition can. A breath of cold in the heat, with you through every summer day.
Desc2:
The reason why it's considered to have commemorative value is mostly due to a promise made by the manufacturer: "Collect 6 consecutively numbered cans for a gold bar."
Everyone went all in for the six-can family pack, but no one has ever seen a can with a number ending in 0 or 5.
